== Alismatales
- Aquatic or semi-aquatic herbs (e.g., _Sagittaria_, _Hydrilla_).
- Some have reduced flowers and lack vessels.
- **Araceae** (Aroids): Spathe and spadix inflorescence (e.g., _Philodendron_, _Anthurium_).

