== Basal Eudicots
- **Ranunculales**: _Ranunculus_ (buttercup), Papaveraceae (poppies).
  - Often have numerous free stamens and carpels.
- **Proteales**: _Platanus_ (sycamore), _Nelumbo_ (lotus).

#figure(
  image(images.at("23-24").path, width: 50%),
  caption: [#images.at("23-24").caption]
