== Caryophyllales
- Core Caryophyllales (Cacti, Carnations, Amaranths).
- **Betalain pigments** (instead of anthocyanins).
- **Perisperm** (nutritive tissue from nucellus).
- P-type sieve tube plastids with protein crystals.
- Adapted to stress/arid environments (succulence, C4/CAM photosynthesis).

